ng the coca flavoring agent sold to the cocacola company stepan extracts cocaine from the coca leaves which it sells to mallinckrodt inc a st louis pharmaceutical manufacturer that is the only company in the united states licensed to purify the product for medicinal use see links for more information  benson drew coca kick in drinks spurs export fears   dope wagons ncpediaorg   cocacola your health – you and your familys gda questions answered cocacolacouk april   retrieved march     gene a spiller  caffeine content of some cola beverages crc isbn    offices  bottling plants archived from the original on february   retrieved january     what is the difference between cocacola enterprises and the cocacola company archived from the original on october   retrieved december     coca cola macedonia makes the best coke macedoniaonlineeu june   retrieved march     stafford leon september   cocacola to spend  billion to grow globally the atlanta journalconstitution retrieved january     will weissert may   cuba stocks us brands despite embargo usa today associated press retrieved august     julian ryall august   cocacola denies cracking north korea the telegraph london retrieved august     a b liebesny herbert j  the law of the near and middle east readings cases and materials albany state university of new york press pp –   coca cola company — red spencerian script archived from the original on january     frank robinson creator of the cocacola logo retrieved december     a b inventory earl r dean collection vigo county public library retrieved december     lundy betty  the bottle pdf american heritage inc pp – issn    snopes urban legend of the cocacola bottle shape snopescom retrieved march     see eg lawrence m friedman american law in the th century new haven yale university press  – and jay m feinman law  everything you need to know about the american legal system rev ed new york oxford university press  –  cocacola light gets dressed by another designer karl lagerfel